text: Dergachevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Pervomaysky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 298 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 48 km from Sterlitamak, 20 km from Pervomayskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Dergachevka
